snippet.title: Antichamber by Voetiem in 13:28 - Corona Relief Done Quick
snippet.description:
Runner introduction starts at 0:08
Run starts at 1:50
Any% starts at 16:30
Commentary is provided by Capitiano
SmoothOperative is host

This speedrun was recorded during Corona Relief Done Quick, a three day charity speedrun marathon raising money for Direct Relief. Corona Relief Done Quick is just one of the many charity marathons organized by Games Done Quick. For more information on Corona Relief Done Quick, find us at: https://gamesdonequick.com
